{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 2935917, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 558013, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "因为它自己说自己是神", "timestamp": 1636876706, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2935937, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 558013, "reply_to": 2935917, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 耶稣可没说", "timestamp": 1636876884, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2935950, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 558013, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "因为一神教里面只有一位神。所以展现了神迹的耶稣只能是神。\n当然也可以不是。就像伊斯兰教解释耶稣的神迹都是上帝与他同在", "timestamp": 1636876942, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2936002, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 558013, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "先是犯了贪婪之罪的……，emmm，额，好吧我编不下去了", "timestamp": 1636877417, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2936024, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 558013, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "认为他是神的一派主要地认为他是真理的审判者（弥赛亚），比先知的级别还要高。实际上耶稣到底该不该具有神性是引发过大讨论的，主流神学认为耶稣是神，但耶稣不是神的观点也在一部分派系中得以保留。所以直接认定耶稣是神，并以此作为假想事实来讨论是不正确的。", "timestamp": 1636877583, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2936035, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 558013, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "圣子实际上也不是特指耶稣其人，而是指耶稣身上传达的上帝之言，否则三位一体没法保证。", "timestamp": 1636877688, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 4, "pid": 558013, "reply": 6, "tag": null, "text": "耶稣为什么是神？", "timestamp": 1636876349, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1636877686, "url": "", "vote": {}}}